text: Rudawa may refer to the following places in Poland: *Rudawa (river), a river in southern Poland *Rudawa, Lesser Poland Voivodeship (south Poland) *Rudawa, Kłodzko County in Lower Silesian Voivodeship (south-west Poland) *Rudawa, Wołów County in Lower Silesian Voivodeship (south-west Poland) *Rudawa, Świętokrzyskie Voivodeship (south-central Poland) *Rudawa, Opole Voivodeship (south-west Poland)
title: Rudawa
